{"tid":1182450,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"頭先落街買盒燒味飯","createTime":"2019-06-02T07:55:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-02T08:33:42.000Z","uid":215355,"like":35,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"cf7449f7880d6d73f7220d8329b816a701e81fb8","tid":1182450,"uid":215355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T07:55:04.000Z","msg":"前面有幾個看更阿姐買緊飯咁我排隊啦，突然間後面又多幾個啱啱放工嘅阿姐原本諗住排隊嘅，跟住斬燒味嗰位嬸嬸認得嗰啲阿姐問佢係咪要雞翼同叉燒，後面嗰堆粉腸竟然走上前諗住打我尖畀錢然後揀餸，好彩我同斬燒味個位嬸嬸都有啲交情佢畀我揀咗餸先，我一嘢就買曬所有叉燒同雞翼畀咗成三百幾蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我臨走嗰陣見到嗰幾個阿姐黑口黑面喺度話我冇家教爆我粗，我心諗抵你死想打我尖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你今晚食西北風啦"},{"pid":"78d2e8e3d2123872e8aa20ba987fcbdcc3d4fb27","tid":1182450,"uid":186844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T07:58:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d13898df95bfa02ec9c3df1c351555b0e360e18c","tid":1182450,"uid":224123,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T08:09:21.000Z","msg":"舒壓po<br />\n<br />\n睇完好舒服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf628c22d6dfce34a7d5d50d4a0e440721350849","tid":1182450,"uid":215355,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d13898df95bfa02ec9c3df1c351555b0e360e18c","tid":1182450,"uid":224123,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T08:09:21.000Z","msg":"舒壓po<br />\n<br />\n睇完好舒服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T08:19:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 最憎打尖"},{"pid":"55c09cf5ab006df0e75ee57273f6a1c4b536f002","tid":1182450,"uid":56999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T08:20:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a26cfc123782e3df757ee72e16aac4e97d211430","tid":1182450,"uid":241021,"like":0